<h1>The Beauty of Cricket</h1>
<p>
    This website will explore the various aspects of Cricket. Includes the rules, how to play, fun facts, and other miscellaneous topics related to cricket. Just as a general explanation, cricket is the 2nd most watched sport in the world with over 2.5 billion fans all over the world. Cricket was first introduced in England during the time of Saxons or Norman times by children. It started off being called "craic" which translates to "fun games." Cricket was mainly a children's game until adults started taking interest in the sport. It is believed that cricket derives from bowls, a game where a batsmen stops the ball from reaching its target by hitting it away.
</p>
